author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at "Chat Control" once again. You all know online safety and privacy is incredibly important to me as I consider the Internet the last bastion of true freedom. The world is rapidly implementing numerous laws globally to erode our privacy in messaging and the info we can access.  These laws are being quietly slipped through, and we must resist or lose control forever. Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
title: I Told You Guys To Fight Back... Now It's Getting Too Late...
